## 📦 Installation

### 1. Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/hackwithme144/proscan.git
cd proscan
```

### 2. Ensure Python is installed

```bash
python3 --version
```

### 3. Install dependencies (if any)

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 4. Run the tool

```bash
python3 proscan.py -t 192.168.1.1
```
